Class AbstractModificationRecordPo<K extends Key>

Type Parameters:
K -
All Implemented Interfaces:
ModificationRecord, PersistentObject<K>, Serializable
public abstract class AbstractModificationRecordPo<K extends Key>
extends AbstractBasePo<K>
implements ModificationRecord

AbstractBasePo with ModificationRecord. There is no need to set explicitly the last modification user id. The tidy() method will set the user id of the current Bo2Session as last modification user to any child AbstractModificationRecordPo where it is empty.
